🎶 Headed to the Montauk Music Festival? Your ticket’s worth more than just good vibes! 🎟️

Flash your festival ticket and get a complimentary Montaukila Tequila Soda OR your favorite Montauk Brewing Co. beer — on us at either LUNCH location from Friday, May 16th through Sunday, May 18th🍹🍺

Because great music deserves great drinks. Cheers to Montauk! 🌊🍻
